author: wn.com
title: Biden offers new account of his advice to Obama on bin Laden raid
text: WASHINGTON (Reuters) - U.S. Vice President Joe Biden said on Tuesday he advised President Barack Obama in May 2011 to go ahead with the raid that killed al Qaeda leader Osama bin Laden, contradicting his past comments about the discussions leading up to the operation.
